==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
Of Hebrew origin (compare [[כּנּרת]] {{HH|3672}}); 

===Pronunciation===
*Γεννησαρέτ / Gennēsaret / ghen-nay-sar-et'

===Proper noun===
'''Γεννησαρέτ'''

# Gennesaret (that is, [[Kinnereth]]), a lake and plain in [[Palestine]]: - [[Gennesaret]].

